product.name: Dragon's Dogma - PRE-OWNED - PlayStation 3
product.description: You've battled enemy forces in sweeping multiplayer campaigns, mastered complex combat techniques and blasted level caps to smithereens. But just when you thought you knew everything there was to know about the action genre, an unprecedented force has seized the gaming world ? and forever revolutionized the art of combat. Step into a realm that rivals your own in realism, detail and freedom, and lose yourself in the epic quest that's destined to rewrite the pages of gaming history. In this world where mythical creatures roam at large and merciless enemies threaten to murder your ambition, you make the decisions ? and you suffer the consequences. Envisioned by the masterminds behind Resident Evil 4 and Devil May Cry 4, Dragon's Dogma redefines the action genre, immersing you deeper than ever into the inner workings of an open world. A fierce warrior, you've set out on a perilous campaign to track down and destroy an enigmatic, bloodthirsty dragon. But you're not alone. A party of three independently fighting pawns back up your mission, offering their own individual strengths and weaknesses to the battlefield. Manage your allies carefully, choosing one to constantly train at your side, and reserving the others for when they're needed most. If you're willing, offer to share your pawn with a friend via the PlayStation Network, and you just may benefit from your generosity. In this mythical realm, goblins, griffins and dragons abound, but beware ? Dragon's Dogma is no fairytale. These creatures of lore appear in their truest, most grisly forms, stirring at different hours of the day and night to impose an ever-unpredictable challenge. As you delve deeper into the storyline, you must master the most intricate details of combat ? down to the weight of your sword, material of your armor and placement of your strike ? in order to complete the mission with your life. Featuring a richly detailed environment, hundreds of fully voiced NPCs and an uncanny 24-hour day/night cycle, this gripping new franchise isn't just a game ? it will become your Dogma.

product.description: SynopsisThe furious fighting action of the Dead or Alive franchise returns with this new installment. Utilizing a unique triangle battle system, Dead or Alive 5 cranks the exciting gameplay up a notch to keep you on your toes. Choose to battle from a roster of fighters that includes Ryu Hayabusa, Hayate, Ayane, Hitomi and more, and unleash powerful combos, devastating Power Blows and overwhelming counters to dominate your opponents. Dead or Alive 5 returns the thrilling, amped-up fighting action you've come to expect from the popular franchise. Dead or Alive 5 utilizes a unique triangle system to structure fights, where strikes beat throws, throws beat holds and holds beat strikes. Vito, the son of a poor Italian immigrant, longs to throw off the shackles of poverty that have held him down his entire life. Already well practiced in petty crime, he begins to aspire to a higher criminal art: organized crime. Lured by the wealth and power that come with Mob ties, Vito and his childhood friend Joe will find themselves spiraling ever deeper into the hold of the Mafia as they struggle to make their names in the streets of an unforgiving city ? or die trying. Mafia II thrusts you into a world bullet-riddled with violence and intrigue. In this follow-up to the intense Mafia, the dark and unforgiving world of the Mob comes alive with gangster movie-style narrative power. Claw your way to the top of the criminal underworld as you engage in stunning car-to-car gunfights, white-knuckled hand-to-hand combat and intense gunplay. With a script from the writing team of the original Mafia and a soundtrack rich with music that evokes the game's 1950s setting, Mafia II immerses you fully in the Mob experience in all its brutality and inescapability.

product.name: NBA 2K8 - PRE-OWNED - Xbox 360

Sport your gravity-defying moves from city to city in Dunk Contest challenges, where only the baddest and the best can unlock new dunks, props and players in multiplayer and online modes. Keep the screaming crowds interested or say goodbye to your career. The groundbreaking Signature Style feature returns, this time with hundreds of new shooting, dribbling and passing animations. Change the playing style of your favorite team members and create custom moves and dunk packages to send the fans into a frenzy. Scoring isn't the only consideration; new defensive controls enable you to play tighter defense on the ball handler and run other defensive sets that shut down the offense. product.name: Charm Girls Club: My Fashion Mall - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS

Can you transform the entire mall into the most sought-after hangout spot around? In Charm Girls Club: My Fashion Mall, you decide the best way to bring the mall to a cooler state. Complete various Mall Drama missions to earn you charms and fashions. Set up a beauty bar for makeovers, pour lattes for the customers, primp cute puppies at the pet store and more. Complete 10 fantastic mini games throughout the mall's four main zones: Mall Munchies, Fashion Zone, Beauty Block and Gifts Galore. See if you can collect more than 50 virtual charms as you and your gal pals increase the mall's coolness factor.

product.name: Ghostbusters: The Video Game - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii

Equipped with a variety of unique weapons and gadgets, you will hunt, fight and capture a wide range of uncanny phantasms and demons in an all-new funny and frightening battle to save New York City from its latest paranormal plague. Ghostbusters: The Video Game features the original film cast from the classic Ghostbusters films, including Bill Murray, Dan Aykroyd, Harold Ramis and Ernie Hudson. Aykroyd and Ramis also return to write the script and storyline for the game. Enter an exciting gameplay environment that authentically recreates the whimsical time period of the film and expands the lore and supernatural events that seemingly plague New York City. Join the team as either a male or female rookie, and experience cooperative ghostbusting action in two-player co-op split-screen campaign mode.

But the West isn't about to go down without a fight. Damnation draws you into a gorgeously rendered steampunk environment inspired by the American Civil War. You'll wield retro-futuristic weaponry and vehicles to defend your territory against a malevolent industrial force. As the hero Rourke, perform amazing daredevil feats across massive, open environments that unfold both horizontally and vertically. Push yourself to the limit as you leap across chasms, swing on ropes and chains, scale massive buildings and engage in frantic gun fights with ruthless artificial intelligence foes who attack from any direction. As Chopin drifts between this life and the next, the story unfolds in a tale of good and evil, love and betrayal. Will the characters in Chopin's dream survive the battles ahead? In Eternal Sonata, explore an immersive world filled with fantastically detailed 3D graphics, anime-style cel-shading and the sweet compositions of Frederic Chopin. Don't be fooled by the beauty that surrounds you; cunning enemies that can change shape will engage you in intense battles loaded with free-roaming and turn-based action. Overcome these adversaries with strategic use of light and darkness and by adjusting your special attacks to each situation. The drama culminates in the final three hours of Chopin's life, where you will learn the fate of the boy and girl in the composer's dream.

Playing as one of the three factions, you must master your deadly abilities if you wish to survive. This year, an American cultural icon celebrates his third decade of indulging gamers in dot-chomping, ghost-fleeing arcade entertainment, and he's doing it with a big bash. Bursting out of the arcade scene and into your living room in bright color and vivid graphics, Pac-Man is bringing party-style competition and strategic gameplay to your Wii in an all-new adventure for nostalgic gamers and arcade amateurs alike. Pac-Man Party takes the eternal hero of the arcade classic into a birthday-themed world full of fun new characters and wacky challenges for the whole family. That wily Pac-Man will have you and your friends and family climbing mountains, rolling giant snowballs, teeing up for golf and of course gobbling up goodies in more than 45 different mini games that stretch across various game boards. Whether you plunge right into the fierce competition in Mini Game mode or take time to explore the immersive Story mode, it'll take strategy ? and some Power Cookies ? to stay on top in this crazy adventure. Get the whole crew together for a big challenge in a Party mode that pits you against your friends in a race for points, and collect property along the way to build your wealth. And what would a birthday party be without a walk down memory lane? Relive the arcade magic that pulled you in in the first place as you play the classic versions of Pac-Man, Galaga and Dig Dug in this celebratory collection.

Will you team up with the heroic Autobots to save the planet that made you, or will you embrace the idea of universal domination and join the tyrannical Decepticon forces? You may just find yourself embroiled in a battle neither side will truly win. Transform between robot, car, jet, tank and truck forms as you find the most effective way to beat your enemy. With advanced multiplayer options, you can join up with friends to fight in teams or go head-to-head to determine ultimate control. All new sci-fi art and improved character visualizations take the franchise to the next level as you immerse yourself in this epic conflict. The city lies strewn with enormous, hanging symbiote hives and infected symbiotes. Only Spider-Man can save the city from certain doom ? but he has his own shadows to confront. As he battles against the ominous alien invasion, will he choose the grace and speed of Spidey's traditional Red Suit and align himself with other great heroes? Or will he heed the siren's call of the Black Suit and all the sinister power it provides, thus choosing the path of the vigilante instead? In Spider-Man: Web of Shadows, you'll encounter a city and a hero with greater depth than ever before in a Spider-Man game. Scale buildings that climb into the sky and engage in ferocious vertical battles on city walls. Destroy storefronts and vehicles as you use anything and everything in your vicinity as a weapon. Switch between the Black Suit and the Red Suit to take advantage of each suit's specific powers, and earn experience points you can use to upgrade either suit, thus enhancing the abilities you find most advantageous. Join forces with legendary Marvel heroes and villains to combat the alien menace, but beware ? the game's morality meter tracks the public's reaction to your decisions. Do you prefer a citizenry that embraces you as a hero, or one that cowers in fear before your terrible power? Your choice to act as hero or vigilante will affect how the war of the Big Apple vs. alien invasion ends.

product.name: The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisThe legendary Dragon Emperor of China has lain peacefully in his tomb for a great many years. But when Alex O'Connell discovers the tomb, a sequence of events is set in motion that could change the world forever. Ambitious warlord Yang is well-acquainted with the tales of the Emperor and is determined to raise him from the dead. Soon, Yang and the reanimated Emperor are teamed up in a deadly quest to locate the Pool of Eternal Life and restore the Emperor to full power, and thereafter attempt to take over the world. Only the O'Connells can put a stop to this, but they're going to face a variety of dangerous obstacles along the way. Do you have what it takes to overcome ancient threats, unlock hidden treasures and ultimately prevent the evil Dragon Emperor from becoming immortal? Join Rick and Evy O'Connell, their grown son Alex and other popular characters from the Mummy franchise for heart-pounding action and excitement in The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor. Play as either Rick or Alex as you travel to six exotic locations from the movie, facing terrifying challenges along the way, including reanimated terracotta soldiers, vengeful ancient demigods and a giant fire-breathing dragon. Collect more than a dozen period weapons to protect yourself, including Webley revolvers and Garand rifles, and experience fast-paced action that switches seamlessly between hand-to-hand combat and ranged gunplay. If you manage to survive, eventually you'll face the Dragon Emperor himself in a climactic battle in the Foundation Chamber beneath the Great Wall of China as you attempt to keep the Emperor from crossing the Wall and becoming immortal. Enter the Tomb of the Dragon Emperor and prepare for spectacular action like you can only find in the world of The Mummy.

Choose from sports cars, bikes, monster trucks, planes and even a giant banana to perform special maneuvers and speed your way to the checkered flag. Can you keep up in this high-speed showdown? Sonic & SEGA All Stars Racing lets you race at high speeds through visually stunning courses, including Sonic Seaside Hill, Curien Mansion and Blizzard Castle. Choose from 20 different SEGA characters like Sonic, Tails, AiAi and Amigo, and unleash a variety of pick-up weapons or unique character moves to gain an advantage to grab that checkered flag. Grand Prix, Arcade and Time Attack game modes deliver hours of comic, high-speed entertainment ? or challenge friends in online action. Kick it into high gear and hug the curves to cross the finish line first.

product.name: The Princess and the Frog - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS

From genuine New Orleans-style music and cooking to the fun of playing frog games in the bayou, The Princess and the Frog steeps you in the charm and excitement of the animated film. Roam the irresistible world of New Orleans and the bayou as The Princess and the Frog whisks you away on a magical adventure. Play as Tiana and Ray, using Ray's special flying abilities to help you soar to new heights. Rely on your courage and daring to embark on special quests and outwit your enemies. Savor the delicious culture of New Orleans as you cook regional cuisine in multiple activities, and even discover real recipes. Then gather up to three friends for wireless ad-hoc gameplay that lets you make beautiful music together and save it in the game's jukebox.

product.name: Need for Speed: Nitro - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisThe world dissolves into a blur outside your windows as you push the gas pedal to the floor and unleash all the power your car has to offer. You rocket past your competitor, taking the lead just as you head into the final stretch toward the finish line. Your hands are steady on the wheel and your heart pounds in anticipation of the victory that is nearly within your grasp. Your tires eat up the ground, taking you closer to the finish line with every second that passes, and in the rear-view mirror you can see your closest opponent trying to rally. Will your burst of speed be enough to carry you through to ultimate triumph? Push your vehicle to its limits as you achieve daring, breakneck speeds in Need for Speed: Nitro. Experience the exhilaration of adrenaline-fueled, high-stakes street racing in which you'll take corners at 200 mph and do all you can to vault past your opponents. product.name: Pheasants Forever: Wingshooter - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisYou stalk through the tall, dried grass ? swiftly, silently, only making the slightest of rustles as leaves brush against your feet. Your faithful hound at your side, weapon in hand, you dominate the landscape with the confidence of a true hunter ? you are the peak of the food chain, the king of this meadow. Suddenly, you stop. Your keen eyes spot the teal green head. Your dog's keen ears hear its talons snapping a twig. Your prey has appeared. Scope to your eye, trigger to your finger, heart pounding in your chest you wait for the perfect moment. A flutter, a bang, a thud ? a success. The fields and swamps are teeming with a rich harvest of game: pheasants, duck, quail, turkey ? the list goes on and on. The chill of late autumn is in the air and the time is right; the fruits of nature are yours for the picking, and you have all the tools you need. Arm yourself with a powerful gun, load up with ammo and layer on the orange ? it's hunting season, and the wild game has never faced a hunter as sharp as you. In Pheasants Forever: Wingshooter, more than 20 different types of game are at your disposal as you prowl the environment with a loyal hunting dog and authentic firearms. Hone your hawk-eye hunting skills in mini games that take your target shooting, gun reloading and quick drawing to the limit. Hit the trails with a friend in head-to-head competitions and prove you've got the guns to gather the most game. One thing's for sure as you trek into the wild ? the feathers are going to fly.

Experience the magic of the first four stories under the spell of LEGO-style gameplay. Build the adventure from the cupboard under the stairs to the Triwizard Tournament as Harry, Hermione and Ron master their magic, mix potions, soar on broomsticks and earn house points while trying to save the wizarding world from the return of He-Who-Must-Not-Be-Named. It's your job to make sure your baby girl gets a good start in life, so offer all the love and care you possibly can. Feed, change, bathe and play with her as much as you can to let your baby know just how much you love her. Teach your baby a wide variety of skills while you learn from new experiences with every game. Give her all the tender-loving care and affection you can and watch your child blossom as she grows.

product.name: Cabela's Dangerous Hunts 2011 - Xbox 360

All of a sudden, with the snap of a twig, the maned head whips toward your hiding spot and his sinewy legs tense, prepared to strike. With a monster track list composed of songs from Guitar Hero, Guitar Hero II, Guitar Hero Encore: Rocks the 80s and Guitar Hero III: Legends of Rock, Guitar Hero Smash Hits brings together some of the hottest tracks from the original guitar-centered games, allowing you to jam along to updated note tracks and experience all-new gameplay for drums and microphone. Balancing the two sides of her life has long been a challenge, but when Hannah Montana's popularity begins to rocket beyond all expectations, Miley's pop star persona threatens to take over her life. Now her dad is taking her back to her hometown of Crowley Corners, Tennessee, to take a break from the limelight and reconnect with her roots. Will it be just the dose of reality Hannah Montana needs, or will Miley find herself pining for the rock star lifestyle? Hannah Montana: The Movie, based on the Walt Disney Pictures feature film, lets you experience Miley Stewart's secret double life for yourself. product.name: Dance Dance Revolution: Hottest Party - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii

Designed specifically for the groundbreaking Nintendo Wii console, this Dance Dance Revolution version gets even more physical than before, as dancers can use the Wii Remote and Nunchuk controller for even more intense interaction possibilities. With an all-new soundtrack and totally redesigned gameplay, Hottest Party takes exciting dancing action to new levels of fun. With support for up to four-player simultaneous play, Hottest Party lets you challenge friends while keeping the action fast and furious. Swing the Wii Remote to send obstructions to your opponents or to achieve greater body interaction. New mini games and options give you multiple ways to play, while an all-new soundtrack provides licensed hits from the past four decades. Turn any day or night into a sizzling good time with Dance Dance Revolution: Hottest Party.

product.name: Rock Band Metal Track Pack - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii

Packing a full 20 tracks on one disc, this standalone game makes it easy for you to form your own awesome heavy metal band and rock out to songs like Bullet for My Valentine's Walking the Demon, Godsmack's I Stand Alone, Judas Priest's Screaming for Vengeance and Queens of the Stone Age's 3's and 7's. Show you have the skills to take your place among the pantheon of heavy metal legends as you perform on guitar, drums, bass or vocals to songs that have helped define a genre. Rock Band Metal Track Pack gives you the chance to live out your heavy metal ambitions. This fully functional game includes all the features you love about Rock Band, including Solo and Band Tour modes, Quickplay, Tug of War, Score Duel and song unlock progression, all to the head-banging beat of an awesome metal soundtrack. Use your instrument controllers to play any of 20 tracks based on the original master recordings, including six tracks brand new to the Rock Band series: Blue Oyster Cult's Transmaniacon MC, Hawkwind's Master of the Universe, I Mother Earth's Levitate, Motorhead's Killed by Death '08, Nazareth's Hair of the Dog and Rage Against the Machine's Bulls on Parade.

product.name: Little League World Series Baseball 2009 - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisStep right up to show you've got big talent in the Little League. In Little League World Series Baseball 2009, all the fun, excitement and competition of Little League Baseball comes alive with thrilling enhancements for an all-new season. Improved controls, additional stadiums, teams and more immerse you in the thrill of this classic pastime as you take the bat in hand, step up to the plate and swing for the fences. Do you have what it takes to lead your team to victory? Little League equals big fun in Little League World Series Baseball 2009. Demonstrate your baseball talents in six thrilling challenges, including four of the best from the prior season and two brand-new challenges. New talent vs. talent face-offs heat up the competition, and an expanded World Series mode, including a full team editor, regional tournaments and six new stadiums, steeps you in all the intense excitement of this iconic championship. Customize your player's batting, pitching and fielding style with the enhanced character creator. Feel like a pro as legendary announcers Brent Musburger and Gary Thorne track your moves play-by-play, and unlock all-new cards for added excitement and challenges.

product.name: Amazing Adventures: The Forgotten Ruins - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisDeep in the heart of a remote land, a mysterious treasure sits waiting to be found. Along with the other members of your archaeological expedition, you are in search of a lost Mayan temple. Inside the temple reside secrets the likes of which you can only dream about. Use your sharp eyes and clever mind to find the clues and objects you need to reach a priceless reward. In Amazing Adventures: The Forgotten Ruins, you will embark on a journey that will take you through intriguing and exotic locales. Keep your eyes peeled for more than 1,600 objects hidden throughout 70 exciting seek-and-solve puzzles. Decipher notes in a mysterious journal, and piece together clues that will lead you to the legendary treasure that awaits at the end of your quest.

product.name: Spider-Man: Web of Shadows - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii

A deadly symbiote invasion has descended, and the city lies strewn with enormous, hanging symbiote hives and infected symbiotes. Only Spider-Man can save the city from certain doom ? but he has his own shadows to confront. As he battles against the ominous alien invasion, will he choose the grace and speed of Spidey's traditional Red Suit and align himself with other great heroes? Or will he heed the siren's call of the Black Suit and all the sinister power it provides, thus choosing the path of the vigilante instead? In Spider-Man: Web of Shadows, you'll encounter a city and a hero with greater depth than ever before in a Spider-Man game. Scale buildings that climb into the sky and engage in ferocious vertical battles on city walls. Destroy storefronts and vehicles as you use anything and everything in your vicinity as a weapon. Switch between the Black Suit and the Red Suit to take advantage of each suit's specific powers, and earn experience points you can use to upgrade either suit, thus enhancing the abilities you find most advantageous. Join forces with legendary Marvel heroes and villains to combat the alien menace, but beware ? the game's morality meter tracks the public's reaction to your decisions. Do you prefer a citizenry that embraces you as a hero, or one that cowers in fear before your terrible power? In Spider-Man: Web of Shadows, the decision is yours to make.

Brunswick Pro Bowling features 10 immersive environments that test your stamina and require your best bowling strategy. product.name: Zoo Tycoon 2 DS - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisIf you love the zoo-building features of the Zoo Tycoon series, check out the new possibilities of Zoo Tycoon 2 DS. You'll still have total control over your very own zoo, but with more animals, habitats and structures than ever before. There's also a multiplayer option that lets you test a friend's zoo-building skills and trade zoos. More than 35 animals will be entrusted to you, including fantasy animals such as yetis and unicorns. Keep a watchful eye on your zoo's inner workings and discover amazing unlockable items as you progress. When it comes to this zoo, you're top dog. Enter Zoo Designer mode to build your dream zoo from the ground up. Which habitats will be best for the animals in your care? Which structures will you need to build to keep these creatures from escaping? Make the right decisions, then enter Zoo Director mode to manage it all. There you'll need to run a successful zoo by attracting sponsors and holding special events. Not ready to call all the shots? Just enter the mini games of Zookeeper mode and use the stylus to feed, brush, clean, pet and nurse beautiful 3D animals.

product.name: Jojo's Fashion Show - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS

Now Jojo is staging a comeback, but does she still have what it takes to dominate the runway? Only with your help can she mix and match clothing and accessories to put together killer outfits that will make her the darling of the fashion world once again. Put your own sense of style and flair to the test in Jojo's Fashion Show. Coordinate and accessorize your way to stardom as you design knockout looks in an array of styles, from Western to bridal to eveningwear. Dress models in thousands of different looks, and watch your creations come alive on the runway as you race against time to unlock exciting new clothing items and accessories. Show off your unique fashion sense and prove to the world that you have the style it takes to become a fashion phenomenon.

product.name: Cate West: The Vanishing Files - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS

When a series of bizarre, seemingly unsolvable crimes paralyze the city and leave the citizens baffled, Cate is called in to apply her own unique mode of investigation in the quest for answers. But can even Cate get to the bottom of crimes so mysterious they've been dubbed The Vanishing Files? Cate West: The Vanishing Files plunges you into a compelling mystery as you assist Cate as she pieces together the clues to these puzzling and intriguing cases over 15 mysterious chapters. Scour 57 unique backgrounds to uncover more than 1,000 clues, and apply five different investigation techniques to help you sift through the evidence and eventually identify the criminal. With Cate's abilities and your detective skills, you just might be able to help Cate piece together the mystery ? not to mention identify a link between The Vanishing Files and an unsolved mystery in her own past.

Now, the aliens have returned to complete their genocidal goal of annihilating mankind in a deluge of fire and pain. Neither the local law enforcement nor the US military machine has been able to put down the alien threat and it seems like you've been chosen to do what they can't. Don the Nanosuit 2 and arm yourself with an arsenal of technologically advanced weapons to decimate the invading hordes before humanity goes up in flames. Can you survive this Crysis? Planet Earth is in ruins and now the aliens have returned to hit humanity where it hurts ? New York City. In Crysis 2, you will be outfitted with the combat-enhancing Nanosuit 2, allowing you to absorb devastating blows and delve into a flood of creatures not from this world. Resurrect the world as you once knew it by battling the invaders that infest the Big Apple. As a super soldier, you must rage across the urban landscape of New York City to handle this Crysis before it's too late.

product.name: Army of Two: The 40th Day - PRE-OWNED - Xbox 360

In the heart of this chaotic environment, the powerful Army of Two has emerged once more. As Rios and Salem roam the ravaged city districts in pursuit of the secrets behind the man-made disaster, they'll find themselves caught up in a dangerous game that will test their teamwork to the limits. Army of Two: The 40th Day delivers an immersive cooperative gameplay experience. Team up with a friend to prove you have the teamwork and strategy it will take to triumph in a city embroiled in a nightmarish scenario. Continue the fight online in an array of explosive multiplayer modes, including the four-player Extraction bonus mode in which you'll move from point to point throughout the city, taking on waves of determined enemies. Take advantage of incredible advanced weapon customization to heighten your firepower in the heat of battle as you strive to unlock the secrets of the mysterious 40th Day.

product.name: God of War III - PRE-OWNED - PlayStation 3
product.description: SynopsisIn an age of Gods and men, the ex-Spartan warrior Kratos refuses to cede power to the deities of Olympus. Betrayed and enraged, Kratos is determined to wreak his vengeance on the callous Gods. Over the course of his quest, he will solve complex puzzles and face off against some of mythology's darkest and most dangerous creatures. But these will only whet his appetite for annihilation, for Kratos has a larger goal in mind: toppling the mighty Zeus, the ruler of the Gods, and destroying Olympus once and for all. Return to the brutal world of ancient Greek mythology in God of War III. Take on the role of the powerful Kratos and arm yourself with his deadly double-chained blades as you pursue your goal of ultimate destruction. Picking up where the action of God of War II left off, this epic conclusion to the mythological trilogy thrusts you into battle against the Army of Olympus at the reignition of the Great War. Scale the heights of Mount Olympus on the back of the mighty Titan Gaia to rain carnage on the Gods of the Greek pantheon and achieve revenge against all those who have betrayed you.

product.name: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - PRE-OWNED - PlayStation 3
product.description: SynopsisFight for survival and shoot your way to mission success as the acclaimed Call of Duty franchise makes its triumphant return. Exploding with the realism and intensity that have become the hallmarks of this gripping series, you'll lay waste to your enemies as hails of gunfire erupt. Move out for intense action and make sure you're prepared to answer the Call of Duty. This harrowing sequel to Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare thrusts you once more into the haze of battle. Arm yourself with sophisticated tools of destruction and get ready to stare death in the face as you enter a raging conflict. Experience the rigors of battle and struggle against long odds to seize victory. The awesome power of war comes alive in all its grit and glory in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2.

As three different ghosts lead Scrooge through a supernatural nocturnal adventure, you'll discover a wealth of compelling puzzles and intriguing adventures that evoke the spirit of this timeless tale. Connect with beloved characters like never before, and discover the wonders of a charming new holiday tradition. The classic Dickens novel comes alive in a whole new way with Disney's A Christmas Carol, based on the Robert Zemeckis animated film. Interact with a variety of favorite characters from the feature film, and see Scrooge's world come alive with gorgeous detail in immersive animated cutscenes. Aunt Lucy is depending on you to help her heal the ailing animals inside the zoo as well as improve the zoo's rating and attract new exotic animals for a fresh exhibit. It's your job to bring the zoo and its precious inhabitants back to life and to save the animals' home. Expertly wield your Wii Remote to battle parasitic pests, tooth decay and disease. Show your love for the patients by patting, feeding and treating them in their enclosures. product.description: Charge your mobile phone with this lithium-ion battery that features 3.7V of power and a 1000 mAh capacity for reliable, long-lasting use.

product.description: Generate prints quickly with this HP Officejet 7500A e-All-in-One printer that offers print speeds up to 33 ppm* in black and 32 ppm* in color for fast results. The 2.4" LCD display features a TouchSmart frame to help simplify operation. Generate prints quickly with this HP Officejet 7500A e-All-in-One printer that offers print speeds up to 33 ppm* in black and 32 ppm* in color for fast results. The 2.4" LCD display features a TouchSmart frame to help simplify operation.

product.name: SimAnimals Africa - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisInteract with lions, elephants, gorillas and other amazing animals in SimAnimals Africa. The environment here can be harsh and unforgiving, so you'll need to make friends with the local wildlife to survive. Get to know the animals, learn about their unique personalities and keep them happy and healthy. Earn their trust, for they have unique abilities that, when combined with your wit, will prove crucial to your collective survival. It's all up to you in this vast animal kingdom, so make good choices to keep everyone living in peace and harmony. Navigate and customize unexplored savannahs, jungles, river deltas and other areas filled with insects and interesting plant life. Along the way, keep watch for rare items you need to progress through the adventure. Then use your trusty backpack to store and carry collected items. Once you've found every item in these fun Collection games, you'll earn badges as a reward. Continue to improve as overseer of the animals and you'll see new animal types emerge. You can also earn the ability to play as a baby or full-grown version of an animal in the Direct Control mode.

product.name: Animal Genius - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisIf you're curious about the creatures that roam the Earth, you'll love Animal Genius. It features fascinating facts and fun trivia about animals from all over the planet. See how much you know about fish, mammals and other animals in more than 140 rounds of play and five addictive games. Increase your knowledge about each species with tons of entertaining exercises. This challenging game takes you through habitats around the globe, such as the tropical rain forest, the frozen arctic and vast oceans. Enjoy viewing hundreds of realistic photographs that deepen your learning experience. Each game features different play patterns to keep up your interest levels, and there are also chances to earn extra points in the bonus rounds. Be ready at any moment for a random Animal Alert that will ask you a question on the spot.

product.name: Shrek Forever After: The Final Chapter - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisShrek, Fiona, Donkey and Puss In Boots are back in Shrek Forever After, the final chapter in the Shrek story. Shrek longs for the days when he was a "real ogre" and not the family man he is today. Making a deal with the slick-talking Rumpelstiltskin, Shrek is transported to an alternate world where ogres are hunted, Rumpelstiltskin is King and Shrek and Fiona have never met. Fight to save your friends, the land of Far, Far Away from the mischievous miscreant, Rumpelstiltskin and reclaim your one true love. Team up with your friends in the ultimate Shrek game, based on DreamWorks Animation's final Shrek movie. Play as Shrek, Puss In Boots, Donkey and Fiona to out-smart, out-fight, and out-play that crafty Rumpelstiltskin. Team up with up to four of your friends and be transported to an alternate version of Far, Far Away in this quest to save your home. Use each character's unique abilities to solve puzzles and unleash their powerful fighting moves to defeat enemies in exciting gameplay. Switch between Shrek's normal world and the alternate reality for double the adventure, and re-discover your inner ogre to restore your world to its former glory.

product.name: Dawn of Discovery - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisIt is the year 1404, and the kingdom is suffering under the effects of a severe drought and a brutal famine. In despair, King George turns to his two sons, calling upon them to seek out new means of gathering resources to meet the needs of his subjects. Edward favors an aggressive approach, while William proposes a more peaceful solution. With the king's blessing, William embarks on a journey into the lands to the south of the kingdom and returns with powerful new technologies, such as a water pump that aids in irrigation of dry land. But William's solution will prove only the beginning of a long process of nurturing this civilization to full power. In Dawn of Discovery, you are tasked with the challenge of sustaining your own vast society. Explore an intricately detailed world as you seek out ways to cultivate a civilization. Mingle with neighboring cultures to learn how they have mastered the challenge of maintaining a prosperous society, and establish trade posts and trade routes to further the economic success of your own nation. Consult an in-game encyclopedia and an intelligent help system to aid you in your decision-making, and apply your creativity and determination to fulfill the needs of your people and help your society flourish.

product.name: Lowepro - Pro Runner X350 All Weather (AW) Camera Backpack - Black
product.description: Carry your digital SLR camera in this backpack that converts to a roller for travel-friendly options. Polyester and nylon materials offer a durable, lightweight design.

product.name: Madagascar: Escape 2 Africa - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisReturn to the wild and wacky world of the hit animated film Madagascar and delve into the excitement with a cast of faces both familiar and new. Madagascar: Escape 2 Africa, based on the sequel to the film, invites you to explore an all-new adventure set in a dazzling and exotic environment. Get ready to encounter new characters and challenges, all infused with the same zany fun that you loved about the first film and video game in the series. Explore the thrilling world of Madagascar as any of your favorite characters from the film, including Alex, Marty, Gloria, Melman and even the crafty penguins or wacky King Julien. Take advantage of the various characters' unique combat moves to turn each situation to your advantage. Make your way through 12 exciting levels where you'll get to explore new environments like the Watering Hole and the volcano. Share the fun with a friend courtesy of a variety of mini games that afford plenty of multiplayer action.

product.name: The Hardy Boys: Treasure on the Tracks - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisThe Hardy Boys are about to embark on an adventure that will take them into the heart of a mystery veiled in the mists of time. They've boarded the Royal Express traveling from Paris to St. Petersburg and are hot on the trail of the Romanov family treasure, long shrouded in secrecy. Will they be able to shed light on the family's secrets and free someone from a life that until now seemed forever to be trapped in fading memories? In The Hardy Boys: Treasure on the Tracks, you'll play as Frank and Joe Hardy as they use their keen investigative skills to solve an enduring mystery. Perform your own amateur detective work as you snoop through train cars, interrogate suspects, evade pursuers and more. Explore intriguing European landscapes as the Royal Express takes you on a journey through cities such as Vienna, Prague and Warsaw. You can even examine the mystery from a different perspective by switching characters to play as a highly trained international spy you'll encounter en route to your destination.

product.name: Black & Decker - Wet/Dry Bagless Cordless Hand Vac - White
product.description: Quickly clean wet or dry spills in your car, boat or home with this cordless wet/dry hand vac that features a removable dirt bowl and a washable filter for thorough cleaning and simple operation.

product.name: Sonic Colors - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisThey may be small and they may be wispy ? but don't you dare call them wimpy. The nefarious Dr. Eggman has uncovered the secret of a strange and powerful alien race called Wisps, and now he's out to harness their Color energy for his own evil plan for world domination. Only one hero can foil the doctor's nefarious schemes, and that hero sports a color of his own ? blue. Jet into the fantastical world of the Wisps as everyone's favorite blue speed demon and prepare for a truly colorful adventure that will accelerate you to all-new levels. Sonic Colors invites you into a mysterious astro-themed amusement park, where you'll race, ride and throttle full-speed into danger for the greater cause. Blast through obstacles at faster speeds than ever, beam away enemies with sharp-shooting lasers and drill through the ground thanks to a little help from the Wisps' Color Powers. Explore a fantastical factory in the sky and venture into lush vegetation, discovering hidden pathways along the way. The power of colorful energy beckons, but this is no "somewhere over the rainbow" ? if you can't use the kaleidoscopic abilities for good, Dr. Eggman's evil color scheme might just lead to a worldwide fading. Can you color yourself a hero in time to save the planet?

product.name: Sid Meier's Civilization Revolution - PRE-OWNED - Xbox 360
product.description: SynopsisYou love the addictive gameplay of the famous Civilization series. Civilization Revolution gives you the opportunity to experience the epic world-building of Civilization in a new way. Designed from the ground up by the legendary Sid Meier and his team at Firaxis, you'll enjoy new graphics, gameplay and control that take full advantage of today's leading gaming platforms. Choose from 16 civilizations from throughout history, including Africa, America and China. Play as a famous leader, such as Abe Lincoln, Otto von Bismark and Mao Zedong, then compete against other leaders as you create your own history. Traverse the world to explore and discover relics, technologies, barbarians and more. Accessible maps and a streamlined time scale treat you to quicker games and constant action. Real-time interaction allows leaders and advisors to actively communicate with you, even turning and pointing to items as they speak. A variety of single-player and multiplayer options give you many ways to build and lead an empire.

product.name: Family Party: 30 Great Games - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisBreak out the fun with over 30 exciting games to choose from. Family Party: 30 Great Games combines everything from track and field events and classic playground games to feats of strength and brain games. Bring together your friends and family for Wii-style fun and classic competition as you go head-to-head in an array of games so varied, everyone at your party is certain to find at least one at which he or she excels. Family Party features 30 diverse and challenging games, each optimized for play with the Wii Remote. Leap over hurdles, jump rope, spin plates, shoot laser guns, climb ropes, play memory games and more as you make your way through these fun-filled contests. Choose from a dozen unique characters and face off against up to three additional players or computer-controlled opponents. Simultaneous and turn-based play ensure that everyone gets a chance to excel, while the medal system rewards high achievers.

product.name: Halo: Reach - PRE-OWNED - Xbox 360
product.description: Learn more about Halo: Reach. (Flash demo) SynopsisThe planet Reach is the last line of defense against the encroaching Covenant's ultimate goal of destroying Earth. Sacrifice and courage are the traits that make you and your Spartan brothers part of an elite group of soldiers known as Noble Team. In this tragic and heroic story that sets the stage for the Halo saga, you are faced with impossible odds to save countless lives and defend Reach from annihilation. If your mission fails, then humanity faces an inevitable demise. Halo: Reach places you in the role of a member of the elite Noble Team engaging in battle against the Covenant. You must defend Reach against the invading forces to protect humanity from devastation. Your weapons, armor and deadly skills are as unique as each of the Spartan soldiers' personalities. Prepare for this epic storyline alone or team up with up to three friends and launch a co-op assault against the incredibly cunning AI which adds a level of complexity to each encounter and battle. The multiplayer action that Halo fans have come to expect delivers once again by setting a new standard of competitive online gameplay, customization, matchmaking and community integration. Experience the adventure and excitement like never before in this incredible installment of the ground-breaking Halo saga.

product.name: KitchenAid - Architect Series II 15" 50-Lb Built-In Icemaker - Stainless-Steel
product.description: This icemaker is capable of producing up to 50 lbs. of ice in 24 hours to make sure you always have plenty of ice on hand. A 25-lb. easy-access storage bin holds a steady supply of ice.

product.name: Backyard Football '10 - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisYou love the strategy and intensity of NFL football, watching as massive players collide on the field. Now get ready to get back to basics as you show off your own pigskin prowess in wacky neighborhood-style football games. Suit up for action and join in the fray alongside the pint-size forms of pro players as you behold some of your favorite NFL superstars as you've never seen them before. Backyard Football '10 features pros from all 32 NFL teams, shrunk down to kid size and ready for crazy backyard-style football action. Use cool power moves and control to dominate the action as you enjoy intense single games or the ongoing thrill of season play. Discover an array of fun unlockables and wacky powerups, and share the fun with your friends in zany two-on-two co-op action.

product.name: Stanley - 6 Gal Wet/Dry Vacuum
product.description: Ensure your floors are clean with this wet/dry vacuum that features up to 4-1/2 HP for thorough cleaning and a stainless-steel tank for durability. The blower port lets you use the vacuum as a blower for versatile use.

product.name: Boelter - Buffalo Sabres Portable Party Fridge
product.description: Take your tailgating party to the next level with this portable party fridge that holds up to 24 cans of your favorite beverage. The Buffalo Sabres logo adds a stylish look to the fridge and allows you to show your team pride before or after the game.

product.name: DreamWorks 2-in-1 Party Pack with Shrek's Carnival Craze and Madagascar Kartz - Nintendo DS
product.description: SynopsisShoot, aim and throw your way to victory with the lovably abrasive Shrek and his fairytale crew. In Shrek's Carnival Craze Party Games, silliness reigns as you vie for the highest score in dozens of action-packed carnival games. Assume the role of one of your favorite characters from the three Shrek films and become part of the big green ogre's delightful world. Run wild with your favorite characters from the Madagascar films in a whole new way. In Madagascar Kartz, you'll join Alex, Marty, Gloria and others as they engage in thrilling, high-speed kart racing that will send them zipping across a series of wild and crazy tracks. Get ready to unleash your own inner wild animal as you careen your way around a variety of challenging courses and demonstrate your most over-the-top moves. Get ready for an exciting party with the DreamWorks 2-in-1 Party Pack which features Shrek's Carnival Craze Party Games and Madagascar Kartz. In Shrek's Carnival Craze Party Games, you can play as characters like Shrek, Fiona, Donkey and Puss in Boots, each featuring their actual voices. Put your precision to the test in Pinocchio's Ring Toss or show your strength in Rapunzel's Hair Climb. Thrilling multiplayer action lets you battle it out in head-to-head competition or unite in cooperative team play. Endure the absurdity until you complete all the party games and you'll unlock Shrek's Swamp. Once you've become King or Queen of the carnival, take the wheel of any of several crazy karts as you race into action across 18 zany tracks based on hilarious scenes from the Madagascar movies. Perform awesome moves like high-flying jumps, flips and rolls, earning points for your most daring maneuvers, and take advantage of a variety of fun powerups that amp up the excitement. Compete against your friends in head-to-head multiplayer gameplay, and unleash additional fun by unlocking secret bonus characters and tracks as you play.

product.name: Microsoft - Xbox 360 4GB Console with Kinect
product.description: Learn more about Xbox 360 4GB Console with Kinect. (Flash demo) You propel through space, your helmet rattling, heart pounding and arms flailing. Suddenly, a meteor zooms directly at you, out of the dark abyss. You fling your body to the left with all of your might, landing safely among the stars ? at the same time you land on your couch. You're in two worlds at once. They've blended together seamlessly. You lift your hand, and a spacecraft roars to life somewhere deep within another galaxy. You brush your foot along your carpet, and a soccer ball flies into the net of a distant field surrounded by screaming fans. Somewhere along the way, the lines between your living room and the exotic, magical, dangerous and far-off worlds of your games have been blurred. The future has arrived, and the Xbox 360 4GB Console with Kinect is delivering it right into your hands. Lose your remote and take command of games, movies and the Internet with the ultimate controller ? you. The power of Kinect's revolutionary full-body tracking recognizes your body, allowing the action of the game to mirror your moves. Feel the vastness of the digital world come alive in lightning-fast, clear HD ? streaming into your room through your TV screen, accompanied by integrated 802.11n Wi-Fi for a fast, easy connection to Xbox Live. Instantly charge into massive multiplayer games online. Download game-enhancing add-ons. Connect with friends through Facebook. View movies in breathtaking detail. All from the lean, quiet, user-tailored 4GB Console. The boundaries have been obliterated. Are you ready to discover the unknown?

product.name: HP - 61 Inkjet Cartridge Twin-Pack - Black, Yellow, Cyan, Magenta
product.description: This combo pack contains 1 black ink cartridge and 1 tricolor ink cartridge, so you can easily replace both cartridges in select HP printers at the same time. The ink produces clear, crisp results for high-quality prints.

product.name: Super Paper Mario - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisThe travels of Paper Mario have taken a new turn ? one that leads him right out of this dimension. When an evil force kidnaps Princess Peach and Bowser, then makes them get married, their union unleashes dark energy with enough power to destroy the universe. Now Mario, along with a little help from Peach and Bowser, must move through 2D and 3D worlds to restore some sort of order to reality. Unforgettable dimensions and hilarious situations make this an adventure unlike anything Mario's ever been through. Super Paper Mario combines many gaming elements to deliver a unique and fun-filled twist on a popular favorite. You'll take part in 2D side-scroller action in the incredible Paper Mario universe and then, with the push of a button, flip into amazing 3D thrills filled with hidden paths, lurking enemies, clever secrets and more. Shake the Wii Remote to pull off fancy moves and even point directly at the screen to get helpful hints. You'll laugh, you'll jump, you'll move in 3D ? all while helping Mario save the universe from sinister silliness.

product.name: KitchenAid - 30" Self-Cleaning Freestanding Double Oven Gas Convection Range - White
product.description: Cook entire meals with this freestanding gas range that features 1 upper standard oven and 1 lower convection oven. The 5 sealed cooktop burners deliver 5,000-16,000 BTUs of heat for quick boiling and heating. Cook entire meals with this freestanding gas range that features 1 upper standard oven and 1 lower convection oven. The 5 sealed cooktop burners deliver 5,000-16,000 BTUs of heat for quick boiling and heating.

product.name: New Play Control: Donkey Kong Jungle Beat - PRE-OWNED - Nintendo Wii
product.description: SynopsisGet ready to go bananas as the legendary Donkey Kong leaps into action on the Wii for his craziest adventure yet. In New Play Control Donkey Kong Jungle Beat, you'll use the fun and intuitive Wii controls to navigate your way through a myriad of exciting levels. Revel in the old-school fun of this perennial favorite combined with new controls that let you execute amazing acrobatic moves like you've never seen before in a Donkey Kong game. New Play Control Donkey Kong Jungle Beat gives you all-new ways to roam the jungle. Use your Wii Remote and Nunchuk controller to swing, soar, swim and perform incredible acrobatic moves, and string moves together to travel like a true daredevil, touching the ground as little as possible. Grab objects, punch with both hands and clap with devastating power as you traverse a gorgeously rendered world filled with fantastic jungles, dazzling caverns and wondrous seas designed to provide thrills for newcomers and longtime fans alike.
